headline: STAA Gains FDA Nod to Expand EVO ICL Age Indication to 60 Years
summary: STAAR Surgical jumps 8% after the FDA expands the EVO ICL age range to 21-60, backed by strong safety data and rising demand for LASIK alternatives.
